public abstract class TemplateValues
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Entity implementation class for Entity: TemplateValues
Container for values used in templates and project environments.
The id is shared with Template and ProjectEnvironment entities and has to be unique amongst all Template and ProjectEnvironment objects.

Author:
Gregor Schumm
